snippet.title: Prepare yourself for this TRY NOT TO LAUGH challenge, it's NOT EASY AT ALL! - Funniest ANIMAL VIDEOS
snippet.description:
Animals are the best entertainment, they make us laugh and happy. This is the most IMPOSSIBLE try not to laugh challenge! You are never bored around animals, they make you smile no matter what! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, pigs, goats, horse, fox, beluga whale,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things and more! So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
